Public version
For the public version, we remove several variables.


Show code
reviews_wide_public &lt;- reviews_wide |&gt; 
  select(-c(tested, citation, outcome_previous_tests, effective, effect_size, comment),
         ) |&gt; 
  select(-starts_with("reviewer_comments"))


We also add the final ranking decided during the plenary meeting between research team and advisory board.
